headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: Principe Lectro
content: Visit the lobby of The Diamond Casino & Resort, and you’ll notice that even they’ve gotten in on the two-wheeled action. In addition to the GTA$, clothing, snacks, RP, and mystery prizes, all those who spin the Lucky Wheel might roll away on the Principe Lectro, an agile little motorbike that yearns to catch some serious airtime.
